        "field-2-label-src": "http://www.metroretrofurniture.com/images/pictures/designer.jpg",
        "field-2-value": "Peter Maly \nSince 1982 Peter Maly has been collaborating with Ligne Roset to create designs that are unpretentious and uncomplicated. These designs range from the Peter Maly bed, the Parallele and Brera cabinetry programs as well as upholstery and accessories like the Reve D`edo collection.",
