        "field-3-value": "(4) Vintage Herman Miller Eames Bikini Wire Chairs \n\nOriginal Cushions \n\nClassic Design \n\nAiry silhouette. The seat is made of cross-woven wires and positioned on a bent-wire, H-style welded base. \n\nOrganic shape. The seat fits the contours of the body. \n\nMultipurpose. Adds artistic interest--and functional seating--to residences and workplaces alike.",
        "field-4-label-src": "http://www.metroretrofurniture.com/images/pictures/dims.jpg",
        "field-4-value": "18 1/4\" Length X 19\" Width X 32 1/2\" Height",
